set_no_steal
Disk World creator help
set_no_steal

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_no_steal -  This method sets the no steal property.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_no_steal(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - the new value of the no_steal property
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the no steal property.  If a shop is set
as no steal, then it cannot be shoplifted.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_steal_difficulty(), query_no_steal(), set_sell_stolen()

.EP

